{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We implemented control variables on the TMT, firm, and industry levels to ensure the validity of our analysis.",
    "On the TMT level, prior research identified an effect of CIO presence within the TMT on AI orientation (Li et al., 2021).",
    "Furthermore, studies assert that CIO and CTO roles sometimes overlap (Haffke et al., 2016; Peppard et al., 2011).",
    "Hence, our analysis includes CIO and CTO presence as binary control variables.",
    "Two independent raters assessed the TMTs of the firms in the data set and coded in a binary manner whether a CIO or CTO was present in the firm based on the role title of the executives."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "On the TMT level, prior research identified an effect of CIO presence within the TMT on AI orientation (Li et al., 2021).",
    "Furthermore, studies assert that CIO and CTO roles sometimes overlap (Haffke et al., 2016; Peppard et al., 2011)."
  ]
